                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d344">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Herdliska</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-07-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 4, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Herdliska, chargé, reports that acting upon the Department’s instructions he
                    has that day communicated the purport of Mr. Hay’s telegram of the 3d, upon the
                    policy of the United States in China, to the Austro-Hungarian foreign
                    office.)</p>
            </div>
